### WhatsApp Personal API - Example Requests
### Replace YOUR_BASE_URL with your actual URL (local: http://localhost:3000, Railway: https://your-app.railway.app)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get QR Code for Authentication
GET {{baseUrl}}/qr

### Send Immediate Message
POST {{baseUrl}}/send
Content-Type: application/json

