### Get All Scheduled Messages
GET {{baseUrl}}/scheduled

### Update a Scheduled Message (replace MESSAGE_ID with actual ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/scheduled/MESSAGE_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Updated message: Good morning! Today is going to be amazing! ‚ú®",
  "schedule": "0 9 * * *",
  "description": "Updated daily morning greeting"
}

### Toggle Scheduled Message (pause/resume)
POST {{baseUrl}}/scheduled/MESSAGE_ID/toggle

### Delete Scheduled Message
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/scheduled/MESSAGE_ID

### Get Schedule Examples
GET {{baseUrl}}/schedule-examples

### Restart WhatsApp Session
POST {{baseUrl}}/restart
